{"tid":2511743,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"案情提「五大訴求」官禁講","createTime":"2021-05-01T06:45:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-01T06:45:12.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"900184b74762976b795e5fdca4ab0039afb4ab96","tid":2511743,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T06:45:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210501/HRNOWZ4TNZH3LC563WDTRCAWKU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210501%2FHRNOWZ4TNZH3LC563WDTRCAWKU%2F&d=TdbSzDXFtRyzmt3f81zqRM5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=bfdb7da6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210501%2FHRNOWZ4TNZH3LC563WDTRCAWKU%2F&h=f55e57e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210501/HRNOWZ4TNZH3LC563WDTRCAWKU/</a><br />\n<br />\n案情提「五大訴求」官禁講<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/dp3PEjjHfHC1vF9eI_UNtyVes8U=/510x286/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ELUV5EYEARFSLEHGTYF427YQ4Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fdp3PEjjHfHC1vF9eI_UNtyVes8U%3D%2F510x286%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FELUV5EYEARFSLEHGTYF427YQ4Y.jpg&h=8662f821&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■梁凱晴昨到庭應訊，認罪還柙。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】控方昨在庭上讀出案情，根據案情，認罪四人黃之鋒、岑敖暉、袁嘉蔚、梁凱晴於六四當日走進被鐵馬圍封的維園，僅手持蠟燭、獻花及接受訪問。當控方讀出有聚集人士曾喊出「五大訴求 缺一不可」等口號時，法官陳廣池隨即打斷，認為相關政治口號與本案無關，毋須向公眾複述。控方同意，只讀出與六四相關的口號。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：悼六四案 四人認罪還柙  黃之鋒庭上高呼「唔好俾世界改變自己」<br />\n<br />\n控辯雙方承認的案情指，支聯會就去年6月4日的六四悼念活動，向警方申請不反對通知書，惟衞生署認為集會會增加市民感染新型肺炎的風險，不建議舉行公眾集會。警方遂以疫情及八人限聚令為由，拒絕支聯會的申請。六四當日，警方及康文署於維園內及附近設立揚聲器，分別提醒公眾不可違反八人限聚令，並警告市民不要參與未經批准的集結，又以鐵馬圍封整個維園。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兩萬人出席 李卓人主持<br />\n<br />\n當日下午，有市民開始於維園內的噴泉廣場聚集。未幾，李卓人、朱凱廸、梁凱晴、岑敖暉亦進入維園內，有人拉開封鎖球場的鐵欄，好讓公眾入內。其後聚集人數逐漸增加，大部份人身穿黑衣及手持蠟燭。各被告亦同樣坐於球場內，朱凱廸當時身穿白衣，梁凱晴及袁嘉蔚則身穿黑衣，三人均手持蠟燭，身旁有白花。<br />\n<br />\n其後梁凱晴及朱凱廸分別接受記者訪問，亦有市民與梁凱晴及岑敖暉合照。約晚上8時，李卓人以揚聲器呼叫「平反八九民運」等口號，眾人支持附和。朱凱廸、黃之鋒、袁嘉蔚將白花遞給李卓人，其後朱及袁又將白花置於地上。<br />\n<br />\n此時約有兩萬人於現場聚集，集會由李卓人主持，眾人最終散去。案情指由於當晚大批人士出入維園，附近交通受到阻礙。各被告明知而參與未經批准集結，亦有公開片段拍攝到案發時的情況。控方讀出承認案情時，曾複述聚集人士呼叫「五大訴求 缺一不可！」等口號，但遭陳官反對，指口號與案無關。控方遂順應法官的要求，略去相關口號。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/wCWVA9EsEolP_3gWaEQHKGuvjjM=/510x437/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KQOLZTDBJJDA7EFEDKQFZOSXX4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FwCWVA9EsEolP_3gWaEQHKGuvjjM%3D%2F510x437%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKQOLZTDBJJDA7EFEDKQFZOSXX4.jpg&h=a3ec4371&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■岑敖暉由囚車押送上庭。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/JCRhLeqh_JZtd1pQ_Jj4eU6jSDg=/510x483/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/AZLE2WEGRRCMDIFTDQL45N2CJA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJCRhLeqh_JZtd1pQ_Jj4eU6jSDg%3D%2F510x483%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FAZLE2WEGRRCMDIFTDQL45N2CJA.jpg&h=ca0c07e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■袁嘉蔚去年在維園悼念六四事件。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/RxSzXC0zL1hCqtugxhtU2iM2x1I=/510x768/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3U42WRTJBJG5ZNUBSSJT42WPFU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FRxSzXC0zL1hCqtugxhtU2iM2x1I%3D%2F510x768%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3U42WRTJBJG5ZNUBSSJT42WPFU.jpg&h=8d701a02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n法官陳廣池"}]}